metadata.name: spring has come! (March)
metadata.description:
The ogre girl was actually a princess who had been captured by the ogre along with chocolate.  
Prince Rabbit, dressed as a one-dimensional man, came to rescue the princess and fed her strawberries to break the ogre's curse.

Then the princess was able to return to her original form and safely return to the castle!

And she lived happily ever after with her rabbit prince!

Happy ending!

..........
